<p>The autonomous AI agent market could reach $35 billion by 2030. If enterprises improve agent orchestration, <a href="https://www.deloitte.com/us/en/insights/industry/technology/technology-media-and-telecom-predictions/2026/ai-agent-orchestration.html">Deloitte estimates</a> that number could climb to $45 billion.</p>
